<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ja">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/stylesheets/form.css">
	<title>入力フォーム</title>
</head>
<body>
<h1 class="form_title">アンケート調査</h1>
<h3 class="form_text">プレゼントの前に簡単なご協力お願いしますm(_ _)m</h3>
<div class="post_block">
<form action="/" method="POST">

  <div class="box_title_block">
    <p class="box_title">年代</p>
  </div>
  <input type="radio" name="age" value="10" required>10代
  <input type="radio" name="age" value="20" required>20代
  <input type="radio" name="age" value="30" required>30代
  <input type="radio" name="age" value="40" required>40代
  <input type="radio" name="age" value="50" required>50代
  <input type="radio" name="age" value="60" required>60代
  <br><br>

  <div class="box_title_block">
    <p class="box_title">行きたいエリア</p>
  </div>
  <div class="box_block">
    <input type="radio" name="Prefectures" value="庄内" required>庄内
    <input type="radio" name="Prefectures" value="最上" required>最上
    <input type="radio" name="Prefectures" value="村山" required>村山
    <input type="radio" name="Prefectures" value="置賜" required>置賜
    <br><br>
  </div>
  <div class="btn_block">
    <button class="btn" type="submit">プレゼントページへ ＞</button>
  </div>
</form>
</div>
</body>
</html>